title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 141-1.1 - Application
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 141-1.1 - Application

State Regulations

Every employer in the building service industry shall pay
to each employee, as defined herein, not less than the minimum wage rates
provided in this Part. Notes
